name: CLAUNECK
description: > CLAUNECK has power over riches, can cause treasures to be found. He can give great riches to he who makes a pact with him, for he is much loved by Lucifer. It is he who causes money to be brought.

name: MUSISIN
description: > MUSISIN has power over great lords, teaches all that happens in the Republics, and the affairs of the Allies.

name: FRIMOST
description: > FRIMOST has power over women and girls, and will help you to obtain their use.

name: KLEPOTH
description: > KLEPOTH makes you see all sorts of dreams and visions.

name: MERSILDE
description: > MERSILDE has the power to transport anyone in an instant, anywhere.

name: CLISTHERT
description: > CLISTHERT allows you to have day or night, whichever you wish, when you desire either.

name: acham
description: > SIRCHADE makes you see all sorts of natural and supernatural animals.

name: HICPACTH
description: > HICPACTH will bring you a person in an instant, though he be far away.

name: HUMOTS
description: > HUMOTS can bring you any book you desire.

name: SEGAL
description: > SEGAL will cause all sorts of prodigies to appear.

name: SURGAT
description: > SURGAT opens every kind of lock.

name: FRUTIMIERE
description: > FRUTIMIERE prepares all kinds of feasts for you.

name: HUICTIIGARAS
description: > HUICTIIGARAS causes sleep in the case of some, and insomnia in others.
